{"word":"G2289 - θανατόω - thanatóō - than-at-o'-o - Become dead","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θανατόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thanatóō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">than-at-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become dead</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - மரணமடை, கொலைசெய், செத்துப்போ, கொல்லப்படு"},{"paragraph":"to put to death"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2288 - θάνατος - thánatos - than'-at-os/2288\">G2288</a>; to <i>kill</i> (literally or figuratively): - become dead, (cause to be) put to death, kill, mortify.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G110/110\">G110</a>, <a href=\"#/G2288/2288\">G2288</a>, <a href=\"#/G2289/2289\">G2289</a>, <a href=\"#/G2348/2348\">G2348</a>, <a href=\"#/G2349/2349\">G2349</a>, <a href=\"#/G4880/4880\">G4880</a>, <a href=\"#/G599/599\">G599</a>"}]}